text: Mamadou Diallo is a Mauritanian freestyle wrestler. Diallo competed for Mauritania at the 1984 Summer Olympics held in Los Angeles, he entered the 90 kg freestyle but lost both of his opening fights and so did not advance to the next round. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Olympic wrestlers of Mauritania Category:Wrestlers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Mauritanian male sport wrestlers Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
